{"name":"Sebastian Scarsdale (Pre-Void)","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Vel Calem, Vanguards","alignment":"Chaotic Neutral","hitDice":"6","armorName":"mage armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"85 (10d8 + 40)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"16","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Arcana Maxima","desc":"[MON] is on his way of becoming one of the most powerful mages in Portum Arcana. After absorbing the powers of the Void, [MON] can now cast two leveled spells a turn."},{"name":"Soulflow","desc":"When [MON] casts a necrotic spell that only targets one creature, he may target another creature."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is a spellcaster. His spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC [INT SAVE], [INT ATK] to hit). [MON] has the following spells prepared:\n\n> Cantrips (at will): _Chill Touch, Sapping Sting, Shocking Grasp_\n> 1st level (4 slots): _Disguise Self, Cause Fear, Inflict Wounds, Magic Missile_\n> 2nd level (3 slots): _Blindness, Mirror Image, Misty Step_\n> 3rd level (2 slots): _Counterspell, Summon Undead, Vampiric Touch_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Corrupt","desc":"[MON] unleashes Void magic to corrupt a point within 60ft. All creatures within a 30ft radius of the point take [3d10] necrotic damage, halved if they succeed a **DC [INT SAVE]** Intelligence Save. Corrupted creatures cannot be healed until the end of their next turn."},{"name":"Power Word: Kill","desc":"[MON] channels the power of the Void. If a creature is down, it instantly dies."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Sebastian","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}